If I'm right,

00:08:20.016 --> 00:08:20.816
that is

00:08:21.200 --> 00:08:22.512
a wet cave.

00:08:37.872 --> 00:08:38.672
Third Uncle.

00:08:44.176 --> 00:08:44.976
Third Uncle.

