Later, I discovered

00:09:58.576 --> 00:10:00.203
it was just a monkey.

00:10:02.203 --> 00:10:04.203
Know how ancient people handled it?

00:10:05.642 --> 00:10:07.762
They'd feed people

00:10:07.762 --> 00:10:09.843
