♪Without measure♪

00:30:32.345 --> 00:30:35.483
♪Behold the uncertainties
you've calculated♪

00:30:35.798 --> 00:30:38.666
♪And the hesitation you arrived with♪

00:30:38.964 --> 00:30:41.810
♪Behold, at last, courage stands alone♪

